OL,3,CMarathon Man Gary McKee reaches
OL,4,Cmilestone in 100 day running challenge
OL,6,FGary McKee is more than halfway
OL,7,Fthrough his latest challenge of
OL,8,Frunning a marathon every day for 100
OL,9,Fdays to raise #100,000 for Hospice at
OL,10,FHome West Cumbria.
OL,12,FGary from Cleator Moor - known to
OL,13,Ffriends and supporters as 'Marathon
OL,14,FMan' - is set to finish the gruelling
OL,15,Fendurance feat by completing the
OL,16,FLondon Marathon on 26 April.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Gary McKee
OL,19,Fsaid: "The challenge is going really
OL,20,Fwell.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
