CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1773940276
OL,3,CMarathon Man Gary McKee reaches
OL,4,Cmilestone in 100 day running challenge
OL,6,F"The conditions have been sketchy and
OL,7,Fwe have been wet more times than we
OL,8,Fhave been dry. There is nothing you
OL,9,Fcan do with that other than dress
OL,10,Faccordingly."
OL,12,FGary has support from the local
OL,13,Fcommunity and fellow runners out
OL,14,Fhelping him along the way.
OL,16,FJoel Pennington said: "I do as much as
OL,17,FI can really, today I am just doing a
OL,18,Fhalf marathon with him. He is
OL,19,Fmotivational, encouraging and an
OL,20,Finspiration to the whole of this
OL,21,Fcommunity."
