OL,3,CMarathon Man Gary McKee reaches
OL,4,Cmilestone in 100 day running challenge
OL,6,FAmy Caddy is part of the support team
OL,7,Fwho are waiting with cups of tea and
OL,8,Fother items to help Gary and his
OL,9,Ffellow runners along the way.
OL,11,FShe said: "We could do with getting
OL,12,Fpeople out at weekends. Everyone is
OL,13,Fwelcome to come and run ands get up
OL,14,Fhere for a cup of tea. Any support is
OL,15,Fwelcome."
